      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUNGY (2) has the hoof on the till after placing in all three starts since a spell. Led from a couple of spots wider and boxed on for third at Shepparton last week so has the pace to take advantage of this nice draw. Race fit now so could break through. SWAYWITHSIERRA (4) is another that is close to a win. Made it five placings on the trot when she came from this barrier for third at Bendigo last week. Big chance to put a win on the board. DEMARTINO (6) is a daughter of leading sire Captaintreacherous from an Art Major mare and makes her debut for Wayne Potter. Runner-up in her last two trials so keep her safe. TAKAO (1) showed improvement for second from this barrier last time out.",
